DNS SRV: 
    dig _xmpp-client._tcp.jabber.org. SRV

DNS NS: + 
    dig example.com NS

DNS A: +
    dig -p 53 domain.com @8.8.8.8

DNS CNAME: + 
    dig -t cname www.bbc.co.uk @8.8.8.8

DNS SOA: +
    dig SOA +multiline yahoo.com @8.8.8.8

DNS AAAA:
    dig mobile.events.data.microsoft.com. AAAA @8.8.8.8 